	  (3.21, CERTI-3_2_6), libRTI/RTIambassador.cc (3.73, CERTI-3_2_6):
	  First implementation of zero lookahead time management services
	  (NERA & TARA addition, NER & TAR update). See task #6898.  Be
	  careful, the Object Management services generate more exceptions
	  (invalid time for a UAV or SI with bad timestamps).

