	* ChangeLog (3.13), RTIA/FederationManagement.cc (3.23),
	  libCERTI/Message.cc (3.35, BEFORE_MERGE_WIN32),
	  libCERTI/MessageBody.cc (3.11, BEFORE_MERGE_WIN32),
